# Cursed Japan ARPG — Technical Data Model & Architecture Spec v1.0

## Overview

This document defines the full TypeScript data model, folder architecture, scene wiring, React/Phaser boundary rules, and key JSON schemas for the Cursed Japan ARPG. It is intended as the authoritative reference for implementation, handed directly to a developer or used with GitHub Copilot.

---

## 1. Folder Architecture

```
/
├── client/
│   ├── public/
│   │   ├── assets/
│   │   │   ├── sprites/           # Phaser sprite sheets (.png + .json atlas)
│   │   │   ├── maps/              # Overworld region background images
│   │   │   ├── ui/                # HUD icons, item frames, rune borders
│   │   │   └── audio/             # BGM and SFX (.mp3 / .ogg)
│   │   └── data/                  # Static game data (JSON schemas)
│   │       ├── weapons.json
│   │       ├── armors.json
│   │       ├── accessories.json
│   │       ├── runes.json
│   │       ├── passiveNodes.json
│   │       ├── bosses.json
│   │       ├── enemies.json
│   │       ├── regions.json
│   │       ├── chapters.json
│   │       ├── affixes.json
│   │       └── craftingRecipes.json
│   │
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── main.tsx               # Entry point: mount React app
│   │   ├── App.tsx                # Top-level router & screen switcher
│   │   │
│   │   ├── engine/                # Engine-agnostic game logic (NO React, NO Phaser)
│   │   │   ├── combat/
│   │   │   │   ├── damageCalc.ts          # Six-stage damage pipeline
│   │   │   │   ├── dotEngine.ts           # DoT tick engine (bypass rules)
│   │   │   │   ├── statusEffects.ts       # Burn, Freeze, Shock, Poison, Bleed etc.
│   │   │   │   ├── hitResolution.ts       # Miss / dodge / hit outcome
│   │   │   │   └── defenseCalc.ts         # Armor / Resist / Barrier / HP pipeline
│   │   │   ├── items/
│   │   │   │   ├── itemFactory.ts         # Generate items from templates + affixes
│   │   │   │   ├── affixRoller.ts         # Roll affixes based on grade + pool
│   │   │   │   ├── dropResolver.ts        # Resolve loot drops from enemies/bosses
│   │   │   │   └── craftingEngine.ts      # Grade upgrade, reroll, essence use
│   │   │   ├── runes/
│   │   │   │   ├── runeValidator.ts       # Check weapon-exclusive rune equip rules
│   │   │   │   ├── skillLinkResolver.ts   # Resolve skill + support link combos
│   │   │   │   └── passiveWebEngine.ts    # Node unlock, path traversal, stat sum
│   │   │   ├── progression/
│   │   │   │   ├── expEngine.ts           # EXP gain, level up, stat growth
│   │   │   │   ├── offlineAccrual.ts      # Offline EXP + material calculation
│   │   │   │   └── chapterGate.ts         # Chapter unlock conditions
│   │   │   └── utils/
│   │   │       ├── mathHelpers.ts         # Clamp, diminishing returns, buckets
│   │   │       └── idGen.ts               # Unique item/entity ID generator
│   │   │
│   │   ├── phaser/                # Phaser 3 scenes (combat presentation only)
│   │   │   ├── PhaserGame.tsx             # React wrapper: mount/destroy Phaser
│   │   │   ├── scenes/
│   │   │   │   ├── PreloadScene.ts        # Asset preload
│   │   │   │   ├── BattleScene.ts         # Main combat scene
│   │   │   │   ├── BossScene.ts           # Boss encounter scene (manual)
│   │   │   │   └── OverworldScene.ts      # Lightweight map node visuals
│   │   │   ├── entities/
│   │   │   │   ├── PlayerSprite.ts        # Player visual representation
│   │   │   │   ├── EnemySprite.ts         # Enemy visual + HP bar
│   │   │   │   └── BossSprite.ts          # Boss visual + phase tracking
│   │   │   ├── hud/
│   │   │   │   ├── BattleHUD.ts           # HP/resource bars in Phaser
│   │   │   │   └── DamageNumbers.ts       # Floating damage text
│   │   │   └── events/
│   │   │       └── PhaserEventBus.ts      # EventEmitter bridge: Phaser <-> React
│   │   │
│   │   ├── store/                 # Zustand global state (React-side)
│   │   │   ├── usePlayerStore.ts          # Character stats, level, EXP
│   │   │   ├── useInventoryStore.ts       # Equipped items, bag, currency
│   │   │   ├── useRuneStore.ts            # Owned runes, equipped skill slots
│   │   │   ├── usePassiveStore.ts         # Passive web node allocations
│   │   │   ├── useMapStore.ts             # Current region, discovered nodes
│   │   │   ├── useChapterStore.ts         # Chapter progress, boss kills
│   │   │   ├── useCraftingStore.ts        # Crafting materials, recipes
│   │   │   └── useOfflineStore.ts         # Last session timestamp, accrued gains
│   │   │
│   │   ├── screens/               # React screens (all meta-game UI)
│   │   │   ├── WorldMapScreen.tsx         # Connected overworld node map
│   │   │   ├── BattleScreen.tsx           # Wrapper for PhaserGame + React HUD
│   │   │   ├── ResultScreen.tsx           # Loot, EXP, rewards after battle
│   │   │   ├── InventoryScreen.tsx        # Gear management, item comparison
│   │   │   ├── RuneScreen.tsx             # Skill rune equip + support links
│   │   │   ├── PassiveWebScreen.tsx       # Spider web passive node UI
│   │   │   ├── CraftingScreen.tsx         # Gear upgrade, reroll, enchanting
│   │   │   ├── BossDetailScreen.tsx       # Boss info + full loot table
│   │   │   ├── OfflineSummaryScreen.tsx   # Offline gains report on login
│   │   │   ├── ShrineScreen.tsx           # Respawn, travel, optional upgrades
│   │   │   ├── CharacterScreen.tsx        # Stats, origin cosmetic, appearance
│   │   │   └── StoryScreen.tsx            # Dialogue, chapter scenes
│   │   │
│   │   ├── components/            # Shared React UI components
│   │   │   ├── ItemCard.tsx               # Item tooltip + rarity display
│   │   │   ├── RuneCard.tsx               # Rune tooltip + element tags
│   │   │   ├── AffixList.tsx              # List of affixes on an item
│   │   │   ├── SkillSlot.tsx              # Active skill slot + support links
│   │   │   ├── PassiveNode.tsx            # Single passive web node
│   │   │   ├── LootTable.tsx              # Boss loot table display
│   │   │   ├── RegionNode.tsx             # Overworld map node button
│   │   │   ├── HPBar.tsx                  # Generic HP/resource bar
│   │   │   ├── DamageTypeTag.tsx          # Fire / Ice / Poison badge
│   │   │   └── ModalWrapper.tsx           # Reusable full-screen modal
│   │   │
│   │   ├── hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
│   │   │   ├── useCombatLoop.ts           # Tick-based idle combat hook
│   │   │   ├── useOfflineAccrual.ts       # Calculate + apply offline gains
│   │   │   ├── useItemEquip.ts            # Equip/unequip validation
│   │   │   ├── useRuneEquip.ts            # Rune equip + weapon rule check
│   │   │   └── useSaveLoad.ts             # JSON save/load to localStorage
│   │   │
│   │   ├── types/                 # All TypeScript type definitions
│   │   │   ├── combat.ts
│   │   │   ├── item.ts
│   │   │   ├── rune.ts
│   │   │   ├── passive.ts
│   │   │   ├── character.ts
│   │   │   ├── region.ts
│   │   │   ├── chapter.ts
│   │   │   ├── enemy.ts
│   │   │   ├── boss.ts
│   │   │   ├── crafting.ts
│   │   │   └── saveState.ts
│   │   │
│   │   └── constants/
│   │       ├── gameBalance.ts             # TTK targets, level caps, affix caps
│   │       ├── damageTypes.ts             # Enum: Physical, Fire, Cold, etc.
│   │       ├── weaponFamilies.ts          # Enum + metadata for weapon types
│   │       └── itemGrades.ts             # Enum: Normal → Holy + slot counts
│   │
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── vite.config.ts
│   └── tsconfig.json
│
├── server/                        # Optional backend (Node/Express or Edge)
│   ├── routes/
